The real `Verify` trait returns `Verdict` directly rather than `Result<Verdict>`, and the gates need a JSON `GatePayload` in the `Engram` body. I’m going to build that signal from `GateConfig.workdir`, detect the build system once, order/filter the supported gates by rung, and short-circuit on failure.
